OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSunak hires ITV journalist 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas communications chief    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prime Minister Rishi Sunak has chosen  
OL,6, ITV News journalist Amber de Botton as 
OL,7, his new director of communications.    
OL,9,FShe will leave the broadcaster, where  
OL,10,Fshe is head of UK news, to run Downing 
OL,11,FStreet's media operation.              
OL,13,FDowning Street confirmed the hire after
OL,14,FITV's political editor Robert Peston   
OL,15,Frevealed his colleague would be joining
OL,16,Fthe prime minister's team.             
OL,18,FIt comes as removal vans were spotted  
OL,19,Fin Downing Street on Saturday as Mr    
OL,20,FSunak and his family moved into No 10. 
